{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_10_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 冷たくて気持ちいい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ジャングル探検ロケ、当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Jungle exploration shoot day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.7600000381
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 1.7600000381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "飛行機と船を乗り継いで、ようやく島に到着か……\nここまで来るだけで疲れたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After connecting flights and boats‚ we finally arrived at the island…\nJust getting here was tiring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.7999999602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか、ロケはここからが本番ですよ\nしゃきっとして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? The real shoot starts from here.\nPlease pull yourself together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.2999999602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜は驚くほどいつも通りだな\nこれから過酷なロケに挑むようには見えないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re surprisingly acting normal‚ Rei.\nYou don't look like you're about to face a harsh shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.5333298808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "この間まで無人島でサバイバルしてましたから\n今更この程度で動じたりしません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surviving on a deserted island until recently‚\nso I won't be fazed by something like this now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今回はスタッフやガイドの方も一緒だし\n水や食べ物も最初から用意してあるので気が楽です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ this time staff and guides are with us‚\nand water and food are prepared from the start‚ so I feel at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.8666666269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは今回が楽と言うより\n前回のサバイバルの環境が厳し過ぎただけなんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than this time being easy‚\nwasn't the survival environment last time just too harsh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.7666666269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに無人島の環境は厳しかったですけど、それ以上に\nみんなが自由過ぎて収拾がつかない方が大変でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The deserted island environment was certainly harsh‚ but even more than that‚\nIt was harder because everyone was so free-spirited and uncontrollable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5329763849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "前もそんなことを言っていたが\nさくら達はそんなにはしゃいでいたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said something like that before‚ but\nwere Sakura and the others really that excited?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 58.9999981801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それはもう！　さくらは無邪気に悪気なく\n毒キノコや酸っぱい木の実ばかり集めてくるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely! Sakura kept innocently gathering\npoisonous mushrooms and sour berries…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.2666648467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "雫は隙あらば持参したカメラで、みんなの\nプライベートショットを撮影しようとするし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku tried to snap everyone’s private moments\nwith the camera she brought whenever she got the chance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は夜寝る前にいきなり\n『無人島で本当にあった怖い話』をし始めるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa suddenly started telling\n\"true scary stories from deserted islands\" right before bed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.6666648467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "一番頼りにしていた遙子さんが\n誰よりも率先してボケてくるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Haruko-san‚ who I was counting on the most‚\nended up goofing around more than anyone else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87.1333315134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはバラエティの仕事が多いから\nつい笑いを取りにいきたくなるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san does a lot of variety show work‚\nso she might instinctively want to go for laughs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "バラエティに馴染み過ぎです！　遙子さんまでボケ\n始めたら止める人間が私しかいなくなるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s way too used to variety shows! When even\nHaruko-san starts being silly‚ I'm the only one left to stop them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6231722871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 100.8333325307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "サニピはみんな陽気で、自由奔放で……\nしっかりしてるのが私しかいないんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in Sunny Peace is cheerful and free-spirited…\nI'm the only reliable one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そういう怜も意外と天然だけどな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Though Rei herself is surprisingly airheaded too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4999991973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 111.6999991973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、みんな世話が焼けるんだから……\n私がいなかったらどうなっていたことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ everyone needs so much looking after…\nI wonder what would have happened if I weren't there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 118.9999991973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（そう言いつつ、みんなのことを話す時の怜は）\n（凄く楽しそうな顔をしているんだよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even as she says that‚ when Rei talks about everyone‚）\n（she has such a happy expression on her face）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだかんだ言いながら、怜もみんなとの）\n（無人島生活を満喫したようで良かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Despite complaining‚ it seems Rei also）\n（enjoyed the deserted island life with everyone‚ which is good）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2537135124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 131.1999991973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ出発するみたいですね\nジャングルに入るので、しっかりついて来て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it looks like we're about to depart.\nWe're entering the jungle‚ so please follow me closely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、{user}さんの服装\nスーツと革靴ですけど大丈夫なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Come to think of it‚ your outfit of\na suit and leather shoes - will you be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 147.866665864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "心配いらないよ\nこう見えて体力には結構自信があるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No need to worry.\nI may not look it‚ but I'm quite confident in my stamina.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8666665475,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.333333300021,
          "startTime": 154.8999998808
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6131964922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.7999998808
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.7999998808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……\nちょ、ちょっと休憩しないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah‚ hah‚ hah…\nSh-shouldn't we take a break…?",
        "id": ""
      },
